[1]
[CODE(CSS)@@en[[[display]]: [[inherit]]]]
により [CODE(CSS)@@en[[[inline]]]] となった 
[CODE(CSS)@@en[[[display]]]]
が [CODE(CSS)@@en[[[position]]: [[absolute]]]]
と一緒にあるとどうなるか

[CODE(DOMm)@@en[[[getComputedStyle]]]]
<http://suika.fam.cx/gate/2007/cssom/viewer?c=.container%20%7B%0A%20%20display%3A%20inline%3B%0A%7D%0Ap%20%7B%0A%20%20display%3A%20inherit%3B%0A%20%20position%3A%20absolute%3B%0A%7D;h=%3Cdiv%20class%3Dcontainer%3E%0A%3Cp%20onclick%3D%22%0A%20%20w%20(getComputedStyle%20(this%2C%20null).display)%3B%0A%22%3EClick%20this%20paragraph%20to%20show%20the%20computed%20value%20of%20the%20'%3Ccode%3Edisplay%3C%2Fcode%3E'%20property.%0A%3C%2Fdiv%3E;p=n;x=style-element>

[CODE(DOMa)@@en[[[currentStyle]]]]
<http://suika.fam.cx/gate/2007/cssom/viewer?c=.container%20%7B%0D%0A%20%20display%3A%20inline%3B%0D%0A%7D%0D%0Ap%20%7B%0D%0A%20%20display%3A%20inherit%3B%0D%0A%20%20position%3A%20absolute%3B%0D%0A%7D;h=%3Cdiv%20class%3Dcontainer%3E%0D%0A%3Cp%20onclick%3D%22%0D%0A%20%20w%20(this.currentStyle.display)%3B%0D%0A%22%3EClick%20this%20paragraph%20to%20show%20the%20computed%20value%20of%20the%20'%3Ccode%3Edisplay%3C%2Fcode%3E'%20property.%0D%0A%3C%2Fdiv%3E;p=n;x=style-element>

